name: FREAKOLOCO! #81
description:
FREAKOLOCO! #81

This is the last living specimen of the carnivorous plant WY.Seriousz.
It was found by Doctor.B when he was a child on his journey through the jungles of AmorZônica in FREAKOLAND! He named her RisaAddd, because she is always making sounds that sound like a human laugh. She is also very strong and can easily knock you out with a headbutt or by swallowing your hands.

Her patterns glow in the dark and may be of a language not yet identified by us, she also smells like shit.

Type: Creature / Edition: 4th / Alignment: Unaligned / Height: 110 Cm / Weight: 32 Kg /  Strength: 90 / Dexterity: 10 /  Constitution: 25 / Intelligence: 20 / Wisdom: 5 / Charisma: 90
